1:15 Starting to set up hugo. First thing I notice when I go to the documentation page is that the first thing they mention in their overview is &ldquo;Hugo&rsquo;s Security Model&rdquo;. Why is security the first thing?
&ldquo;When developing and building your site, the runtime is the hugo executable. Securing a runtime can be a real challenge.&rdquo;
What is a runtime? A runtime is when the program runs. In the case of Hugo, it&rsquo;s when Hugo builds the website&hellip; it makes the static HTML output.
